title: MSB seconds experts within mine action to UNOPS in support of their programs
description: In support of UNOPS:s mine action programme MSB seconds experts. Profiles include but are not limited to; EOD specialists, Medical trainers/coordinators and Information management officers. In Ukraine, UNOPS focuses on building a mine action programme that will contract, deliver and oversee a comprehensive package of mine action solutions, including survey clearance, training and equipment and procurement of goods and services.
